title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jul 14 2022
description:
Midterm Variant spurs remasking of the blue states. Viral video: Shuffling Biden shakes hands with man who isn't there. He gets led by the elbow to a seat, in a scene that looks like it is from a nursing home. Economy crumbling, huge interest rates coming, real estate market cools (C&B talk about their Nashville and Florida recent experiences), average Manhattan rent hits record $5,000 a month. John Bolton brags about planning coups, tells CNN Jan. 6th wasn't one -- and, remember, Clay says, Bolton hates Trump. AOC admits Capitol police let Jan. 6th rioters in. Trump weighs 2024 announcement before the midterms -- or not. Clay and Buck advise against announcing before the midterms since Dems have nothing and that might give them something to use as an issue. C&B's favorite wrestlers.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
